It is with great shock and sadness that we offer our condolences and prayers to the family of Jake Brewer, the husband of our HotAir Editor and Townhall Media family member Mary Katharine Ham.

Jake died as a result of an accident while participating in the Ride to Conquer Cancer bicycle rally and fundraiser. He gave his life while trying to help others, a quality that Jake's friends say is defining about him. Jake passed away yesterday at 34 years of age.

The family and friends of Jake Brewer have launched a GoFundMe project to create an educational fund for their two children, Georgia and the one on the way. Mary Katharine faces some very difficult challenges for her children and herself without Jake, but we can help take worries over education off the table for her. Please donate, if you are able.
